{"tid":2194362,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"護士涉把求診警員資料放上網 被控兩罪本月22日西九龍裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2020-09-08T12:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T05:13:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fd8a1923d1ac333d44530de0d6799c99136ce3","tid":2194362,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/131359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F131359&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=ba61d9fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/131359</a><br />\n<br />\n一名25歲診所登記護士，涉嫌將一名求診的警員個人資料上載到社交媒體，去年8月26日被捕。涉事護士今日被落案控告「目的在於使其本人或他人不誠實獲益而取用電腦」及「披露未經資料使用者同意而取得個人資料」的罪名，案件將於本月22日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。 警方提醒市民，高等法院已頒布兩個臨時禁制令，禁止任何人非法地及故意地披露警務人員及其家人的個人資料，以及禁止任何人在網上平台發布或轉發任何促進、鼓勵或煽動使用或威脅使用暴力的言論，違反禁制令的人士，有機會干犯「藐視法庭」罪。<br />\n<br />\n2020-09-08 20:32:34"},{"pid":"5f3d12c6817cd4b4ad5ecd57875b9c2301ef87d4","tid":2194362,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c95cca1849fe534aceab351649333f817364fc","tid":2194362,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"3a958a306950c9d1222d753747187052df915eaa","tid":2194362,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"唉 各位要小心"},{"pid":"3f6740b0d9c09c128290c2e55d93b07f38a8ce19","tid":2194362,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4fd8a1923d1ac333d44530de0d6799c99136ce3","tid":2194362,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/131359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F131359&d=pZTDRaRh7C